{"tid":2260839,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"校委會通過清華幫做副校  港大生研推翻任命","createTime":"2020-10-28T01:22:12.000Z","updateTime":"2020-10-28T03:12:16.000Z","uid":25558,"like":4,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":4,"replies":[{"pid":"f1a1ce7ee7448948fe63b58bcfb26768f7434235","tid":2260839,"uid":25558,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-10-28T01:22:12.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/local/20201028/PTQ72LQBGRDN3LT26DDUYM6JLM/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2F20201028%2FPTQ72LQBGRDN3LT26DDUYM6JLM%2F&d=BCqMRPjRs%2BrlYbPtDS4RDOm6EOSy25kVi46SvbSXLY8%3D&h=9edddefa\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2F20201028%2FPTQ72LQBGRDN3LT26DDUYM6JLM%2F&h=24346139\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://hk.appledaily.com/local/20201028/PTQ72LQBGRDN3LT26DDUYM6JLM/</a><br />\n<br />\n節錄<br />\n<br />\n校委會通過清華幫做副校 <br />\n港大生研推翻任命<br />\n<br />\n【黨委治校】<br />\n<br />\n相關新聞：柏克萊：申作軍否認黨員<br />\n<br />\n【本報訊】中共急於整頓香港教育界，港大校委會昨晚在一片反對聲中，大比數通過委任兩名清華大學學者申作軍和宮鵬明年1月出任副校長，分別負責研究和學術發展。據悉，申作軍提交陳詞否認共產黨黨員身份，被校委質疑可信性，但校長張翔稱希望校委考慮兩人學術背景，張又澄清與兩人分別僅見過一次面。港大學生會對任命表示遺憾，會研究採取法律行動，嘗試推翻委任決定。<br />\n<br />\n港大校委會昨晚通過兩個副校長和法律學院院長任命。據悉，連同校長張翔及校委會主席李國章在內，有22名校委出席，僅一。。。。。。。。。。<br />\n<br />\n相關新聞：學者︰中共操控港公共機構先例<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/resizer/Ar_ynr_gn2vmvuC42wiiu3zhtN0=/2658x1772/filters:quality(100)/cloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com/appledaily/ISURTS5PHFH7HC5P3DOGCSQSOU.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Fresizer%2FAr_ynr_gn2vmvuC42wiiu3zhtN0%3D%2F2658x1772%2Ffilters%3Aquality%28100%29%2Fcloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com%2Fappledaily%2FISURTS5PHFH7HC5P3DOGCSQSOU.jpg&h=79527981&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n■港大校委會本科生代表李梓成昨與學生會會長葉芷琳等人見記者，對校委會通過任命表示遺憾。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n一票反對 李梓成灑淚<br />\n<br />\n李梓成會後表示對結果深感遺憾，但已忠於自己投反對票，又指兩名副校人選沒顯示出應有的危機應變和應對公眾能力，更一度語帶哽咽地說：「我對眼之所以含住淚水，係因為我對呢個地方愛得深沉。」港大學生會會長葉芷琳在旁安慰，李一度低頭拭淚。<br />\n<br />\n本報取得申作軍遞交校委會的陳詞，重申不是共產黨黨員，亦非黨委，形容是「。。。。。。。。。。。<br />\n<br />\n有委員質疑可信性，惟張翔促委員考慮兩人學術背景而非政治背景，大部份委員同意，至少兩人表明是否黨委不重要。有不願具名。。。。。。。。。。<br />\n<br />\n港大校委會主席李國章會後發聲明，指近期兩位副校人選背景「有諸多傳聞」，二人特意澄清，申作。。。。。。。。。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/resizer/xea9TEx_s0HPhvuMDB0B56Qs_xY=/1182x1772/filters:quality(100)/cloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com/appledaily/O5GZIURAYNEE5C7MWNORWVZBRU.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Fresizer%2Fxea9TEx_s0HPhvuMDB0B56Qs_xY%3D%2F1182x1772%2Ffilters%3Aquality%28100%29%2Fcloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com%2Fappledaily%2FO5GZIURAYNEE5C7MWNORWVZBRU.jpg&h=2e8b611c&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n宮鵬<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n學生會：呢間唔係張翔嘅大學<br />\n<br />\n張翔會後向港大師生及校友發電郵解釋今次副校長風波，澄清與申及宮不相熟，在事件中已盡量避免利益衝突。他。。。。。。。。。。<br />\n<br />\n學生會會長葉芷琳對校委會堅持委任申作軍及宮鵬表示失望和憤怒，認為校委會再一次無視學生聲音和4,200個聯署簽名，任命。。。。。。。。。。<br />\n<br />\n港大學生會昨午在校委會會議前發動靜坐，約50名學生參與，他們高呼「遴選制度不公，力拒黨委治校」口號，其後向教務長遞交4,200個港大學生、教。。。。。。。。。。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/resizer/_LnIviLLAke4O7j_rlQpM2dqh8o=/2209x1051/filters:quality(100)/cloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com/appledaily/APJCXP7NJREJZF73BZIGPWW3G4.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Fresizer%2F_LnIviLLAke4O7j_rlQpM2dqh8o%3D%2F2209x1051%2Ffilters%3Aquality%28100%29%2Fcloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com%2Fappledaily%2FAPJCXP7NJREJZF73BZIGPWW3G4.gif&h=37daea69&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"08e296ce6489df6b869938213c66492ad851d0c6","tid":2260839,"uid":258948,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-10-28T01:30:34.000Z","msg":"就好似港女咁<br />\n你愛得深沉又點<br />\n佢係比個有錢仔拐走左就係走左"},{"pid":"01e8f29f9180279c4482d749425c0e7fbc185a9e","tid":2260839,"uid":51752,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-10-28T03:11:11.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img 